        <fw type="pageNum">Page 1</fw>
          <p corresp='TTP34012264P0' xml:id='OTP34012264P0'>[seal]
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P1' xml:id='OTP34012264P1'><rs ref='#S52728'>Meridian, Miss.</rs>,<lb/>
July 26, 1866.
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P2' xml:id='OTP34012264P2'>Governor:
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P3' xml:id='OTP34012264P3'>On the 25<add place='above'>th</add> of May last <rs ref='#S32138316'>Abram Myer</rs>, <rs ref='#S32074731'>charged</rs> with <rs ref='#S32138546'>aiding and abetting</rs> his brother to <rs ref='#S91669'>set fire</rs> to <rs ref='#S50738'>his</rs> <rs ref='#S32121869'>store</rs> in this place, in order to recover the insurance thereon, <rs ref='#S32123269'>escaped from the officer</rs> in charge and made his way to <rs ref='#S63147'>Memphis</rs>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P4' xml:id='OTP34012264P4'>A telegram from Memphis to-day announces that this <rs ref='#S63177'>fugitive from justice</rs> has been <rs ref='#S62954'>arrested</rs> there and will be held subject to our order
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P5' xml:id='OTP34012264P5'>I would respectfully ask that you make a requisition for the said Abram Myer and place it in the hands of the bearer of this letter—
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P6' xml:id='OTP34012264P6'><rs ref='#S32138547'>Gunius Means</rs>, <rs ref='#S95578'>Depty Sheriff</rs>.
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P7' xml:id='OTP34012264P7'>Very respectively
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012264P8' xml:id='OTP34012264P8'><rs ref='#S32026848'>Jno. Armstrong</rs><lb/>
<rs ref='#S63935'>Mayor</rs> &amp; Ex. Officio <rs ref='#S63172'>J. P.</rs> 
</p>


        </div>
        <pb xml:id="F34012265" n="2" facs="https://cdm17313.contentdm.oclc.org/iiif/2/mdah:39015/full/full/0/default.jpg"/>
        <div xml:id="OTP34012265">
        <fw type="pageNum">Page 2</fw>
          <p corresp='TTP34012265P0' xml:id='OTP34012265P0'>July <hi rend='underline'>28<add place='above'><hi rend='underline'>th</hi></add></hi> 1866<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012265P1' xml:id='OTP34012265P1'>Meridian, Miss,<lb/>
July 26<add place='above'><hi rend='underline'>th</hi></add> 1866<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012265P2' xml:id='OTP34012265P2'><hi rend='underline'>Armstrong</hi>— Jn<add place='above'><hi rend='underline'>o</hi></add><lb/>
Mayor<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012265P3' xml:id='OTP34012265P3'>Letter of—
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012265P4' xml:id='OTP34012265P4'>Requesting requisition on <rs ref='#S32003149'>Executive Authority of Tennessee</rs> for <hi rend='underline'>Abram Myer</hi> fugitive from Justice<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34012265P5' xml:id='OTP34012265P5'>Requisition issued as requested<lb/>
July 28<add place='above'><hi rend='underline'>th</hi></add> 1866,
</p>


